SUMMARY:Poetry Open Mic
DESCRIPTION:April 18\, 2026  // Sign Up + Doors 4pm // Showtime 4:30pm\nPWYC cash at the door\nMORE INFO \n \nJoin hosts Raymond Helkio and Jonathan Freeman for sassy poetry\, performance\, literature and libations! This month our featured artists start with the infamous bill bissett with Lothar Bahr + poet and author Drew McEwan! This is an all-ages\, licensed PWYC event\, allies always welcome! Open mic slots are 3 minutes and if you’d like to read please sign-up at the door. \nDOORS + SIGN-UP 4:00 PM \nShowtime 4:30 PM \n  \nBuddies is a fully accessible venue with barrier-free\, gender-neutral washrooms. Thank you to the kick-ass staff at Buddies In Bad Times Theatre\, Tallulah’s Cabaret\, and The Reading Salon. \nMORE INFO \nhttps://raymondhelkio.com/poetry-open-mic \nhttps://www.facebook.com/groups/809670790166270 \nhttps://www.instagram.com/poetryopenmicto
URL:https://buddiesinbadtimes.com/event/poetry-open-mic-16/
LOCATION:Tallulahs
END:VEVENT
