SUMMARY:Bi-Panic At The Disco
DESCRIPTION:April 18\, 2026  // Show 10pm // $15 – $25\nall prices + fees\nBUY TICKETS \n \nFor BI-PANIC’s 1 year anniversary\, they’ve set Buddies Cabaret as their Target ❌ A night of pure bi-bauchery 🏳️‍🌈 in the heart of Downtown \nTRAXX AND FEELS & SOVEREIGNTY.FM bring you an iconic 2 floor exeperience withanexclusive performance by Jordan Alexander \nJoined by your in-house favourites \nACE DILLINGER \nCHISSMISS CHERRY \nMS.MYLES \nINCOGNITA \nINTROSPKT \n& BATHALA (fka SAKINA) \nLose yourself on this open-format dancefloor and prepare to shake ass to familiar and boundless sounds. From Club classics\, Pop punk\, Jersey club\, Y2K\, Dancehall and HipHop edits to Footwork\, Ghetto Tech\, Bass\, Electronica\, Global Club and soo much more! \nA NIGHT TO REMEMBER FROM 10PM-3AM \n19+ I.D’s MANDATORY \nP.L.U.R. is in full effect. BI-PANIC is an inclusive queer space for folks of all identities. Come as you are. \nHope to see you there! xoxo
URL:https://buddiesinbadtimes.com/event/bi-panic/
LOCATION:Tallulahs
END:VEVENT
END:VCALENDAR